title: Antonio Brown Trade Scare, Case Keenum to Redskins and Trash Takes
itunes:title: Antonio Brown Trade Scare, Case Keenum to Redskins and Trash Takes
description:
Big breaking news with Dan Hanzus kicks off the show following the Case Keenum trade and the missed connection between Antonio Brown and the Bills before a room filled with heroes – Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler are joined by Patrick Claybon to talk Odell Beckham Jr on the Browns dark web (21:15) and the end of the Boogermobile. A fan favorite returns when Patrick breaks down his trash takes(49:27).
